  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>MagiChaos is a bullet hell shooting party game that can be enjoyed by up to four players! Experience the \"Magic\" and \"Chaos\" bullet battles with cute magical girls!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/ca44c97c8986347243ef3c36f3048ba8.poster.avif?t=1709892109\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/ca44c97c8986347243ef3c36f3048ba8.webm?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/ca44c97c8986347243ef3c36f3048ba8.mp4?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find Your Unique Combination!</h2>Choose from over 10 bullet skill types! <br>There are two types: main and sub. Bullets set as main can be charged for a powerful shot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07bb0a3b8d0f4da39f8f97c361dd875d.poster.avif?t=1709892109\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07bb0a3b8d0f4da39f8f97c361dd875d.webm?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07bb0a3b8d0f4da39f8f97c361dd875d.mp4?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Magical girls have unique abilities to tilt battles in their favor. <br>Whether it's creating ice walls or teleporting, let's aim for victory with all sorts of tactics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07f762235a1449f5c20ba39114a800d6.poster.avif?t=1709892109\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07f762235a1449f5c20ba39114a800d6.webm?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07f762235a1449f5c20ba39114a800d6.mp4?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/f07cf8656e99a3c9ace394de01bf2d8d.poster.avif?t=1709892109\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/f07cf8656e99a3c9ace394de01bf2d8d.webm?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/f07cf8656e99a3c9ace394de01bf2d8d.mp4?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "MagiChaos is a bullet hell shooting party game that can be enjoyed by up to four players! Experience the \"Magic\" and \"Chaos\" bullet battles with cute magical girls!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/ca44c97c8986347243ef3c36f3048ba8.poster.avif?t=1709892109\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/ca44c97c8986347243ef3c36f3048ba8.webm?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/ca44c97c8986347243ef3c36f3048ba8.mp4?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find Your Unique Combination!</h2>Choose from over 10 bullet skill types! <br>There are two types: main and sub. Bullets set as main can be charged for a powerful shot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07bb0a3b8d0f4da39f8f97c361dd875d.poster.avif?t=1709892109\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07bb0a3b8d0f4da39f8f97c361dd875d.webm?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07bb0a3b8d0f4da39f8f97c361dd875d.mp4?t=1709892109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Magical girls have unique abilities to tilt battles in their favor. <br>Whether it's creating ice walls or teleporting, let's aim for victory with all sorts of tactics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785220/extras/07f762235